WEBVTT

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:22.500
I knew it all along

00:00:22.830 --> 00:00:26.600
That words were nothing but lies

00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:30.200
Easily forgotten

00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:34.500
Uncertain and vague is this thing

00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:40.140
Screwing the truth

00:00:40.700 --> 00:00:47.870
I run into Magic

00:00:48.770 --> 00:00:53.150
In the summer where sun had disappeared

00:00:53.190 --> 00:00:56.700
All alone I was

00:00:56.900 --> 00:01:00.400
the answer that I came across

00:01:00.400 --> 00:01:02.000
that was

00:01:02.200 --> 00:01:05.000
It was you

00:01:06.120 --> 00:01:09.220
I had found you

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:16.530
the answer that should have been more correct than else
